{"TopicId":152389,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"[Question] Making RCS?","CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T01:36:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T01:36:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen making an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E, do you make a\u00A0\u0027thust transform\u0027 in each of the directions of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E and name each one \u0027RCSTransform\u0027 or some similar thing in Unity?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-11-22T01:37:05Z\u0022 title=\u002211/22/2016 01:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Eskandare\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T03:35:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe so - made a \u0022integrated\u0022 control section back in 1.0.5 - had 16 transforms pointing in 6 directions - all named the same. The Unity setup looked sort of odd - but it worked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T06:46:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860060\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479785724\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022120438\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wasml\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, wasml said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe so - made a \u0022integrated\u0022 control section back in 1.0.5 - had 16 transforms pointing in 6 directions - all named the same. The Unity setup looked sort of odd - but it worked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent! Thank you! Now I can rig my tail rotor correctly. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-22T16:12:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222860202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479797189\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262742\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Eskandare\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Eskandare said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent! Thank you! Now I can rig my tail rotor correctly. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you are only allowed 6 l/r/u/d/b/f\u00A0 transforms per nozzle, or more correctly the game will only recognise that many\u00A0 no matter how many you use\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-23T03:57:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250907\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SpannerMonkey(smce)\u003C/a\u003E You got me curious - I went back and installed 1.0.5 and double checked - all 16 transforms do work on the old part reduction piece (a 2.5m cylinder with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E transforms setup to be like four \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E blocks). Of course this is under KSP 1.0.5\u003C/span\u003E using the old ModuleRCS. I\u0027ll have to modify it and see if it still works in 1.2.1 with ModuleRCSFX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steedcrugeon","CreatedById":168050,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-11-23T11:18:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222861336\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022152389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221479873467\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022120438\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wasml\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, wasml said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250907\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SpannerMonkey(smce)\u003C/a\u003E You got me curious - I went back and installed 1.0.5 and double checked - all 16 transforms do work on the old part reduction piece (a 2.5m cylinder with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E transforms setup to be like four \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E blocks). Of course this is under KSP 1.0.5\u003C/span\u003E using the old ModuleRCS. I\u0027ll have to modify it and see if it still works in 1.2.1 with ModuleRCSFX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have recently created a part for 1.2\u00A0which has 30 \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E transforms on it. they all work as intended in game. However this part does not have the option to disable/enable modes in the editor or in flight (pitch/yaw/roll/translate, those do not have toggles) but I can enable/disable\u00A0\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E as per usual. I suspect this is directly as a result of having more than 6, transforms on a single part.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}